data.description: Welcome to this stunning home located in Hixson! This home features a brand new roof, brand new deck, and brand new windows that includes a lifetime warranty! As you open the front door you will immediately notice and appreciate the real and natural hardwood floors throughout the house. Moving into the kitchen where appliances such as: stove, oven and the refrigerator are included. The kitchen also features a generous sized pantry. In the kitchen is a door leading to the 1 car garage, separated by laundry room/mud room.  This house also features a huge bonus room the same size as the living area, which leads to the double doors of the deck. Stepping into your beautiful open backyard where you can enjoy outside, free to your imagination and creativity! This house has 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, both bathrooms have been updated. With the master featuring the half bathroom.Seller is an immediate family member of the agent.
